          <title>Giants owner John Mara gets another aerial message trashing his team before loss to Ravens</title>
          <description><![CDATA[New York Giants co-owner John Mara received another aerial message trashing his woeful team before Sunday's 35-14 loss to the Baltimore Ravens. It was the second straight week that a plane was hired to circle the stadium in protest of the Giants’ seventh losing season since 2017.]]></description>
